  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 57029160960
    m_Localized: Press <color=red>the spacebar</color> to switch to digging mode.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 785877561344
    m_Localized: "\rPress <color=red>the spacebar</color> to return to detecting 
      mode."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42632781233385472
    m_Localized: Welcome to the site! Explore it and find valuable artifacts!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42632781254356992
    m_Localized: Move forward, backward, and sideways - use the <color=red>WSAD</color>
      keys.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42632781258551296
    m_Localized: Hold the <color=red>Shift</color> key along with the directional
      keys for faster movement.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42632781258551297
    m_Localized: Mouse movement - turn right and left.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42632781258551298
    m_Localized: The left mouse button speeds up coil swinging for more precise target
      localization.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646981177344
    m_Localized: The right mouse button toggles the <color=green>PINPOINT</color>
      mode on and off.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371648
    m_Localized: Left mouse button - dig at the circular marked spot.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371649
    m_Localized: Move the coil slowly and find the strongest signal for safe retrieval
      of the item.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371650
    m_Localized: Great, you found something!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371651
    m_Localized: Hold down the right mouse button and move the mouse to rotate the
      object.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371652
    m_Localized: Left-clicking on a piece of soil will remove it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371653
    m_Localized: Zoom in and out on the object using the mouse wheel.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371654
    m_Localized: Try to identify the uncleaned object and earn bonus points.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371655
    m_Localized: You've cleaned the entire object. Good job!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371656
    m_Localized: You failed to identify the found item.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42698646985371657
    m_Localized: You have correctly identified all categories!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42723011881857024
    m_Localized: Obtain more information about the object in your workspace to earn
      additional points.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42723011881857025
    m_Localized: I don't know
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
